      "beast_baseline": "friend or family? what am i supposed to say to them? \"hey my whole life is a lie and i have nothing left\"? they don't get it. they'll just tell me time heals everything but that feels like such a lie. it just feels like i'm stuck in this dark room and the door is locked and there's no reason to even keep looking for a way out.",
